<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=Edge">
  <meta http-equiv="Cache-Control" content="no-transform ">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
  <script type="text/javascript">
    var CONTEXTPATH='';
    var STATICURL='http://img.kanzhun.com';
    var require = {
      urlArgs : "v=v1.1.31"
    };
  </script>
  <!--[if lte IE 9]>
      <script src="http://s.kanzhun.com/js/html5shiv.js"></script>
      <script src="http://s.kanzhun.com/js/jquery-1.11.0.min.js"></script>
      <!--[if gt IE 9]><!-->
  <script src="http://s.kanzhun.com/js/jquery-2.1.0.min.js"></script>
  <![endif]-->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/v2/css/widget.css" />
  <title>邮箱弹出框</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href=/v2/css/bind_email/bind_email.css />
</head>
<body>
<div class="bind_email">
  <h3>
    绑定邮箱账号并验证，<br>
    即可查看所有完整信息
  </h3>
  <p class="mt15"><a class="auth_btn" href="javascript:;">去绑定或验证邮箱账号</a></p>
</div>
<section class="auth">
  <h3>绑定邮箱账号<a href="javascript:;" class="dialog_close"></a></h3>
  <p class="mt10">请输入邮箱，绑定您现在登录的QQ账号。</p>
  <p class="f_12 grey_66">绑定后，使用QQ账号或者邮箱地址都可以登录到你现有的账号。</p>
  <form action="" method="post" id="">
    <p class="sys_err"><span></span></p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <div>
          <label><i class="user"></i></label><input type="text" class="ifd" placeholder="请输入您的常用邮箱" name="account" ka="register_account"><input type="hidden" name="accountCheck" value="" />
          <p class="err" data-msg="请输入您的常用邮箱！"></p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div>
          <label><i class="pwd"></i></label><input class="ifd" type="password" name="password" placeholder="输入6-14位密码，必须含数字和字母" maxlength="14" ka="register_password">
          <p class="err" data-msg="密码不能为空！"></p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div>
          <label><i class="pwd"></i></label><input class="ifd" type="password" name="confirmPassword" placeholder="密码确认" ka="register_confirmpassword">
          <p class="err" data-msg="确认密码不能为空！"></p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p><input type="submit" value="绑 定" class="auth_btn"></p>
  </form>
</section>
<section class="auth">
  <h3>验证邮箱<a href="javascript:;" class="dialog_close"></a></h3>
  <p class="mt10">您可以激活邮箱完成绑定。</p>
  <p class="red">注：激活验证邮箱后你才可以观看看准网全部内容</p>
  <p class="f_12 grey_66 mt15">我们已将邮件发送至邮箱：renyanhong@126.com<br>
    点击邮件内链接即可完成绑定。</p>
  <p class="mt15"><a class="auth_btn" href="#">登录验证邮箱</a></p>
  <p class="f_12 grey_66 mt15">
    稍等几分钟，若没有收到验证邮件，怎么办？<br>
    1、邮件地址填写错误？<a href="#">重新发送验证邮件；</a><br>
    2、看看是否在邮箱的垃圾邮件、广告邮件目录里；<br>
    3、稍等几分钟还未收到验证邮件？<a href="#">重新发送验证邮件；</a>
  </p>
  <p class="t-center grey_66 mt20">5秒钟后自动跳转</p>
</section>
<section class="auth">
  <h3>验证邮箱<a href="javascript:;" class="dialog_close"></a></h3>
  <p class="mt10">请验证您的邮箱地址，以便查看更多内容</p>
  <ul class="mt15">
    <li>
      <div>
        <input type="text" class="ifd" style="margin-left: 0" placeholder="请输入您的常用邮箱" name="account">
        <p class="err" data-msg="请输入您的常用邮箱！"></p>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p class="f_12 grey_99">可修改现有邮箱地址</p>
  <p class="mt15"><input type="submit" value="验 证 邮 箱" class="auth_btn"></p>
</section>
</body>
</html>